<sect2 id="numtheory-bitlshift">
  <title>nt_bitlshift</title>
  <sect3 id="numtheory-bitlshift-syntax">
    <title>Syntax</title>
    <para>
      =BITLSHIFT(x,n)
    </para>
  </sect3>
  <sect3 id="numtheory-bitlshift-description">
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
      The BITLSHIFT function returns x bit-shifted right by n bits.
      If n is negative, a right shift will in effect be performed.
    </para>
  </sect3>
